  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5114440">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5114440/" class="title-link">写官场小说就跟写色情小说一样</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5114440"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/boular/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1787849-18.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/boular/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">李伟长</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-09-29"
      class="main-meta">2011-09-29 17:01:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5114440_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在我等这样熟读了百本管小说的淫民看来，写官场小说就跟写色情小说一样。色情小说封面，色多了一些，就是色情小说，比较下流低级。色少一些，人情多一些，就是情色小说，比如《金瓶梅》，还相当有文学性。官场小说也一样，权力写多了，就成了权术教科书，很无聊。权力写少一点...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5114440/#comments">(54回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">260有用 / 25没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5114440_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5114440_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
