              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19139604/" class="">第139页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/RamblER/" class=" " title="---·--·-·">---·--·-·</a>
                (少年よ、大志を抱け。)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
